text: девушка со светлыми волосами в светлой одежде сидит на светло-бежевом диване, за ней большое панорамное окно с видом на Москву, над которой пролетает клин самолетов
prompt: score_9, score_8_up, score_8, a young woman with blonde hair wearing a light outfit is sitting on a soft light beige sofa, behind her a large panoramic window offers a view of moscow under which planes fly past, the sky is filled with clouds, adding depth and atmosphere to the cityscape behind, high-quality details capture the textures of her comfortable attire and the plush feel of the sofa, subtle lighting enhances the cozy ambiance within while highlighting the vast urban expanse outside, cinematic quality captures a moment of peaceful introspection as she gazes out at the bustling city life beneath her, the composition balances indoor warmth with outdoor dynamism creating a harmonious blend of relaxation and urban spectacle
